contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox French commune |name = Queaux |region = Poitou-Charentes |department = Vienne |arrondissement = Montmorillon |canton = Isle-Jourdain |INSEE = 86203 |postal code = 86150 |mayor = Dany Richard |term = 2008–2014 |intercommunality = Montmorillonnais |longitude = 0.6686 |latitude = 46.3278 |elevation m = 113 |elevation min m = 72 |elevation max m = 160 |area km2 = 52.64 |population = 618 |population date = 2006 }} '''Queaux''' is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Vienne]] [[Departments of France|department]] in the [[Poitou-Charentes]] [[Regions of France|region]] in western [[France]]. ==See also== *[[Communes of the Vienne department]] ==References== *[http://www.insee.fr/en/home/home_page.asp INSEE] {{reflist}} {{Vienne communes}} [[Category:Communes of Vienne]] {{Vienne-geo-stub}}
